    "causal_summary": "Create a repo-native `sk-improve-agent` system that borrows the good parts of `autoagent-main` without copying its trust boundary. The MVP is evaluator-first and proposal-only: it runs bounded experiments against one canonical source surface, scores candidates independently, records every attempt in an append-only ledger, and blocks canonical file mutation until the scorer and promotion contract are proven.",
